import React from 'react'
import Navigation from "../Navigation"
import SinglePage8Data from "./SinglePage8Data"

import PortfContact from '../All_pages/PortfContact'
import Footer from "../Footer"

const SinglePage8 = () => {
     return (
          <>
               <Navigation />
               <SinglePage8Data/>
     
               <PortfContact />
               <Footer />
             
          </>
     )
}

export default SinglePage8
